        <div class="body">
            <p>You cannot use camelCase in the URL to request the action or controller; you need to normalize it to lowercase, using dots ('.') or dashes ('-'; this is the default and recommended way) to separate words.</p>

<p>In the case of your action, you would refer to it as: /admin/country/get-records-by-country. This will then translate to the method Admin_CountryController::getRecordsByCountryAction().</p>

